cn\/wap720\/90eb2137ly1fi2vjiq180j20et08b0tm.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"list_des\">\n                    <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/7542601858160641_1.html?type=new\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">最帅吹头哥爆红！侧脸像鹿晗 正脸像王俊凯<\/a><\/h3>\n                    <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">近日，浙江金华一理发师因超高颜值爆红网络，开博后，一夜之间涨粉36万。听说，一大堆迷妹排队要去剪头发，95后的小哥哥是浙江丽水人，2年前和朋友一起来到金华工作。<\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"UG_box_l\">\n    <!--微博实时热点-->\n    <h2 class=\"UG_box_title\">微博实时热点<\/h2>\n    <div class=\"UG_contents\">\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/fb6ab501afe3f5a7_0.html?type=grab\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot01\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/fb6ab501afe3f5a7_0.html?type=grab\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/005zaaUoly1fi4c2su0itj30bf0cbt9x.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/fb6ab501afe3f5a7_0.html?type=grab\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">阿杜病历照是假的<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">阿杜病历照是假的 精神状态良好！早前，有媒体报道歌手#阿杜#罹患重度抑郁症，甚至有自杀倾向。对此，阿杜好友已经做出澄清，网络上流传的所谓病历照全是假的，阿杜结婚后状况变好，更不时在群里晒小孩，精神状况良好。阿杜所属唱片公司也表示其工作状况一切正常！ ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/9f2aff752c9bda8f_0.html?type=grab\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot02\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/9f2aff752c9bda8f_0.html?type=grab\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http:\/\/wx4.sinaimg.cn\/large\/4bba2f06ly1fi4c1uup73j20dy07uwf5.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s